tar - compress + backup (archive)

tar - archives

gzip, bzip2 - compress

______________________________________


tar czvf linux.tar.gz linux                   (gzip compress + archive)

tar xvf linux.tar.gz			(uncompress directory)

tar tvf linux.tar.gz			(view contents)

since the archive is compressed, we cannot add files to it.

tar -rvf linux.tar.gz file.txt		(error)



tar jcvf linux.tar.bz2 linux	(bz2 compress + archive)
tar rvf linux.tar.bz2 file.txt   (error)
tar tvf linux.tar.bz2		(list)
tar xvf linux.tar.bz2		(undo)

